Waterloo DC ++

By: Thomas Millar

Version: 0.5

This is an install script that is designed to make it easier for non-technical users to download, install, and configure the ShakesPeer DC++ client for the mac with the University of Waterloo's hub. 

Setup:
	1/	Download the project
	2/	Open the downloaded folder
	3/	Double-Click the installDC++.command file.
	4/	Follow the onscreen steps, enter password when required.
	
